All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.util.Observer, java.io.Serializable
public class RatePerfMonCanvas
extends java.awt.Canvas
implements java.util.Observer

RateGraph Engine receives the GraphData objects from all the receivers, throws it into a GraphData vector and paints the Graph. The vector is used, so I can repaint the graph when the observer pattern notifies the engine that it needs repainting. Skewing is an option to allow the lines representing each receiver to be either next to each other (skewed) or on top of each other.
